<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يُظْلَمُونَ}</span> ... لَا يُنْقَصُونَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتِيلًا}</span> ... قَدْرَ الخَيْطِ الَّذِي يَكُونُ فِي شَقِّ النَّوَاةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَادُوا}</span> ... قَارَبُوا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَيَفْتِنُونَكَ}</span> ... لَيَصْرِفُونَكَ، وَيُوقِعُونَكَ فِي الفِتْنَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِتفْتَرِيَ}</span> ... لِتَخْتَلِقَ، وَتَكْذِبَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَلِيلًا}</span> ... حَبِيبًا خَالِصًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضِعْفَ الْحَيَاةِ}</span> ... عَذَابًا مُضَاعَفًا فِي الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَضِعْفَ الْمَمَاتِ}</span> ... عَذَابًا مُضَاعَفًا فِي الآخِرَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَادُوا}</span> ... قَارَبُوا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَيَسْتَفِزُّونَكَ}</span> ... أَنْ يُخْرِجُوكَ مِنْ مَكَّةَ، بِإِزْعَاجِهِمْ إِيَّاكَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَحْوِيلًا}</span> ... تَغْيِيرًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِدُلُوكِ الشَّمْسِ}</span> ... مِنْ وَقْتِ زَوَالِ الشَّمْسِ عِنْدَ الظَّهِيرَةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَسَقِ اللَّيْلِ}</span> ... ظُلْمَتِهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقُرْآنَ الْفَجْرِ}</span> ... صَلَاةَ الصُّبْحِ الَّتِي تُطَالُ فِيهَا قِرَاءَةُ القُرْآنِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَشْهُودًا}</span> ... تَحْضُرُهَا مَلَائِكَةُ اللَّيْلِ وَالنَّهَارِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَهَجَّدْ}</span> ... قُمْ مِنْ نَوْمِكَ فِي اللَّيْلِ لِلصَّلَاةِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَافِلَةً لَّكَ}</span> ... زِيَادَةً لَكَ فِي عُلُوِّ القَدْرِ، وَرَفْعِ الدَّرَجَاتِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>